snippet.title: Bee Welcome! Teaser Gameplay
snippet.description:
There are lots of bees in the meadow, but only one of them is a guest in your bee hotel! Find her in this relaxing Hidden-Bee game! 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2837750/Bee_Welcome/
